  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/161994740/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u161994740-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="天地有大美。" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/161994740/">天地有大美。</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          刚刚          在读      </div>

      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/btone0808/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2730487-4.jpg" class="pil" alt="麦子" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/btone0808/">麦子</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:历史小说</span><br />

          <span class="">高阳小说文字功底深厚。政商勾结（现代角度来看）题材，格局不高。对当代现实指导意义不大，一是方式迭代高级已不是百余年前所指，二是政商联手从来不是民主政治下的主流经济形态。看过了连连称是，但哪有那么多机缘巧合，权当小说一读，能在这里刷豆瓣，说明：时也，命也。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/73210562/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u73210562-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="幸福袋鼠" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/73210562/">幸福袋鼠</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          想读      </div>

      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
